data.description: Welcome to your dream home on Black Creek Golf Course! Just minutes from the New Hyundai Plant. This custom-built stucco masterpiece offers luxury and comfort. With 4 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a sprawling 3318 square feet, this residence is an epitome of spaciousness and elegance. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the grandeur of the two master suites, each offering unparalleled privacy and opulence. Entertainment is at its finest with a sunroom which provides the perfect spot for relaxation. The expansive living space is ideal for gatherings, featuring seamless flow and stylish design elements. Step outside to your private backyard oasis overlooking the 4th hole. Enjoy serene mornings or entertaining evenings in this picturesque setting. This home is not just beautiful but practical too, with a brand new roof ensuring peace of mind for years to come, and new hardwood floors. Indulge in the lifestyle you deserve with this immaculate custom-built home. Your oasis awaits!
